file.name: echo.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
servers:
  - url: 'https://echo.hightowerlabs.com'
info:
  description: The echo API return the message given.
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Echo API
  contact:
    name: Hightower Labs
    url: 'https://developer.hightowerlabs.com'
    email: developer@hightowerlabs.com
paths:
  /echo:
    post:
      summary: Echo message body
      operationId: echo
      requestBody:
        description: message to echo
        content:
          'application/json':
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Message' 
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Message'
components:
  schemas:
    Message:
      type: object
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
